    <string name="legal_disclaimer_title">Safety &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="legal_disclaimer_text">
        <b>Disclaimer:</b>\n
        Use of this app is at your own risk. Speed limits are based on OpenStreetMap data and may be outdated or incorrect. Always prioritize physical road signs. The developer is not liable for traffic violations, fines, or accidents.\n\n
        <b>Privacy (GDPR):</b>\n
        Location data is processed locally on your device. To fetch speed limits, coordinates are sent anonymously to the Overpass API. No personal identifiers or GPS logs are stored on external servers.\n\n
        <b>Attribution:</b>\n
        Speed limit data © OpenStreetMap contributors.
    </string>
